title: Happy Thanksgiving | Ep. 51

description:
DC is back with the crew just in time to give you a Thanksgiving Episode to listen to when your drunk auntie is getting on your nerves, featuring fan favorite Sheneka Adams. We try to figure out what's wrong with Kanye, get DC used to the new studio, discuss Sheneka's new surgery and everything else in between. Leave a comment and subscribe! #85Southshow
